snippet.title: Game Boy - Star Sweep © 1997 Axela - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
A new kind of Puzzle Game with Quick Chain Reactions!
- Four modes of play: 1-Player, Story, 2-Player, and Attack.
- Story mode offers background of eight different characters involved in the storyline.
- Collect enough star fragments to unlock Special mode.
- Easy to learn but it takes practice to master.
